\subsubsection*{Observed land use/land cover data}
Observed land use/land cover data was obtained from \cite{roy_development_2015}, which provides land use/land cover maps at 100m resolution for 1985, 1995 and 2005 \cite{roy_development_2015}. The map for 2005 was used as the basis for statistical analysis and initialising the land change model, while maps of land use/land cover in 1985 and 1995 were used for validation purposes. The land use/land cover maps are based on multi-temporal data from Landsat \cite{}, IRS 1C-LISS III \cite{} and Resourcesat1 \cite{}. The maps were developed at 30m resolution but aggregated to 100m for distribution. The overall classification accuracy of the 2005 map is more than 90\%. The accuracy of maps for 1985 and 1995 were not explicitly tested due to a lack of historical ground truth points. \\

